FT  29 SEP 92 / Engineering pay rises by 3.2%
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
PAY settlements in the engineering industry averaged 3.2 per cent in August,
according to the latest bulletin of the Engineering Employers Federation.
However the federation said the figure was based on only 25 recorded
settlements. It also said that the July figure has been revised upwards to
3.42 per cent from 3 per cent.
