Canada Trust, Imasco's financial services subsidiary, as a result of the
long recession.
Overall, he said, Imasco was 'on course for a year of good earnings growth.'
For the first half ending June 30, profit was equivalent to CDollars 1.21 a
share, up 16 per cent from a year earlier.
